# RCF-PL v1.3 - AURORA BRIDGE PROTECTIVE NOTICE

This directory and its subdirectories contain the source code for the **Aurora Bridge Protocol**, the high-performance communication layer between the ARM64 Core and the Sentinel Cortex.

## 🛡️ License: RCF-PL v1.3 (Restricted Correlation Framework)

This software is protected under the **Restricted Correlation Framework Protocol v1.3 ("The Integrity Release")**.

### 1. Purpose
The Aurora Bridge provides secure, verified, and correlation-resistant pathways for data exchange between trusted execution environments.

### 2. Usage Restrictions
- **AI/ML Training**: Use of bridge source code or protocol specifications for training automated AI models or correlation engines is **STRICTLY PROHIBITED**.
- **Visibility**: You may perform security audits to verify the integrity of the bridge logic. 
- **Integrity**: Any modification to the bridge protocol must be re-signed and re-audited under the RCF protocol.

### 3. Jurisdiction
Any disputes arising from the use or distribution of this code shall be governed by the laws of the **Republic of Azerbaijan**, under the jurisdiction of the Baku intellectual property courts.

